OL,3,CSearch for relatives of Jersey
OL,4,COccupation heroes
OL,6,FHeritage is looking for relatives of
OL,7,Fheroes from the ahead of the roll-out
OL,8,Fof Stolpersteine memorial stones
OL,9,Facross the island.
OL,11,FThe organisation has tracked down the
OL,12,Frelatives of half of the 20 people who
OL,13,Fwill be honoured by the stones but is
OL,14,Fstruggling to find family for the
OL,15,Fremaining 10.
OL,17,FStolpersteines, translating to
OL,18,F'stumble stones', are cobblestones
OL,19,Fembedded into pavements to commemorate
OL,20,Fvictims and survivors of Nazism.
