OL,6,F"We hope there might be an opportunity
OL,7,Fin the future to add further stones to
OL,8,Fremember people who lived through
OL,9,Fthese difficult years."
OL,11,FIris Prigent's late husband, Gordon,
OL,12,Fwill be commemorated after being
OL,13,Fconscripted to during Jersey's
OL,14,FOccupation.
OL,16,FIris explains: "My husband Gordon
OL,17,Fsuffered greatly as a result of being
OL,18,Fsent to Alderney for refusing to work
OL,19,Ffor the Occupiers.
